belongs_to_collection.name: Soubrettes Services : Tous les films de la série Soubrettes Services

overview: Angel has one goal: to maintain the excellence of the services of its guest house to satisfy its high-end male clientele. Counting on her charming soubrettes, she constantly seeks ways to surprise her boarders. And why not offer them a little game track to spice up their stays? Dedicated bodies and souls, her splendid employees will not spare themselves to offer them the most enjoyable rewards. Whether it's a man-hunting in the woods, a sensual hide-and-seek or under a breakfast table, they will enjoy as much pleasure as they give them. But, victim of his success, will Angel find a new maid who will have the talent and vice necessary to strengthen the ranks of her shock team?
tagline: Underneath their apron, these maids are perfect nymphomaniacs!
title: French Maid Service: French Maids to Share
